Additional files to make the STSdroid work.

Rough notes....:

1) install the pipe webcam demo
2) test it
3) disable nginx 
   systemctl stop nginx
   systemctl disable nginx
4) install rerequsites
apt-get install python3 python3-smbus python3-pip
pip3 install explorerhat
pip3 install flask
pip3 install gevent

5) enable SPI and i2c enable boot to cli in raspi-config

ln -s `pwd`/startPipe.sh ~

6) add startPipe.sh to rc.local
su - pi -c "/home/pi/startPipe.sh"

7) reboot 




